User signs in.
User selects the “Send Messages” button.
System displays a list of all employees.
User selects the recipient.
User types in the message.
User clicks “Enter” to send the message.
System notifies the recipient.

SubFlows
S-4a: If there is no previous chat history, the system creates a new chat thread.
S-4b: If there is an existing chat thread, the system displays the chat history.


